title: Yamileth Solorzano
text: Yamileth Solorzano (born 29 May 1988) is a Salvadoran <a href="boxing">boxer</a>. She competed in the <a href="Boxing%20at%20the%202020%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%20featherweight">women's featherweight event</a> at the <a href="2020%20Summer%20Olympics">2020 Summer Olympics</a>.
